sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Client as "Local browser/test client"
    participant Page as "BlogAI.Web /local-dev"
    participant UiService as "IBlogAiLocalAuthStatusService"
    participant Consumer as "IBlogAiAuthConsumerService"
    participant Auth as "AdventuresAuthDecisionService"
    participant Rendered as "Rendered safe status/correlation metadata"

    Client->>Page: GET /local-dev
    Page->>UiService: GetStatus()
    UiService->>Consumer: Evaluate protected placeholder without dev marker
    Consumer->>Auth: Validate local session
    Auth-->>Consumer: Denied decision with correlation metadata
    Consumer-->>UiService: Display-safe denied decision
    UiService->>Consumer: Evaluate protected placeholder with internal dev marker
    Consumer->>Auth: Login local development request
    Auth-->>Consumer: Allowed decision with safe principal placeholder
    Consumer-->>UiService: Display-safe allowed decision
    UiService-->>Page: Auth status display model
    Page-->>Rendered: Allowed/denied state plus CorrelationId, RequestId, AuthDecisionId
    Rendered-->>Client: 200 OK

    Note over Page,Rendered: Raw dev credential, raw token, and secret sentinel values are not rendered
    Note over Page,Auth: No production auth, login form, OAuth/OpenID/RBAC, persistence, deployment change, or BlogEngine.NET coupling
